{"type": "article", "id": 26721, "title": "石像造型的喇叭", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-12T06:39:31Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145804Zrm0enavyVRpUOzb.JPG", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">来自台湾的设计团队 Tengdimai 从复活节岛上的摩艾石像获得灵感，打造出了一款颇为“石尚”的喇叭。每件的外观均采用手工喷制，在原料中加入了细砂成分以呈现出旧水泥和石头的效果。底座部分则采用了磁铁附着的设计，可以轻松地收纳过长的电线，作为纯摆设时完全看不到外露的线材。石像的嘴巴被设计为耳机的插座，增添了一份喜感。这个喇叭目前处于<a href=\"https://www.zeczec.com/projects/tdm-moai\">众筹</a>阶段，售价为 1450 新台币。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145802Wzdqxy3I78b5j1Oi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145803kQ09Ur6MBTgcbZPR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145803dCOkZ4hImMHAJb7G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145804wCU4GkPx92sAj0hI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}